    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such incredible care of it; it's seriously spotless and drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude0a",
