    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm absolutely thrilled to show you this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
